data.description: Nestled in the welcoming town of Bangor, this beautiful 4-bed, 1.5-bath colonial-style home exudes classic charm and offers a perfect blend of historic elegance and modern comfort. Just 15 minutes from the sandy beaches of Lake Michigan in South Haven. Gather around the wood-burning fireplace, a focal point in the living space that adds a touch of warmth and character. Original wooden floorboards throughout the home showcase the enduring quality. Four generously sized bedrooms on the second floor provide ample space, and built-in closet space ensures practicality and organization. he fenced backyard offers privacy and security, creating a perfect setting for relaxation and outdoor activities. Schedule a visit to explore the timeless charm and coastal proximity it has to offer.
